videos.description: At the end of the first half, Nerlens Noel and Solomon Hill start jawing at each other and the benches get involved before it's deescalated.

videos.description: The Knicks fail to put a hand on the ball while De'Andre Hunter sneaks in for the easy basket late in the third quarter.
